1. controller 
    getTodos()
    getTodo()
    createTodo()
    updateTodo()
    deleteTodo()
2. services
    getTodos service
    getTodo service
    createTodo service
    updateTodo service
    deleteTodo service
3. model   
    connect to mongodb
4. module 
    todoModule so that connect todos module to main app


Features
1. crud operations todos (create, update, read, delete)
2. pagination service side 
3. infinite scrolling 
4. spinner
5. skeleton
6. save data with timestamp
7. add login and register for adding todos
8. comment on todos
9. user profile
10. forgot password
11. loader
12. increate api response
13. decrease number of api call
14. optimise application
15. eslint
16. prettier
17. unit testing
18. internationalization
19. responsive (implement all the foundamental of html, css, sass)
20. add notification if someone commented on your todo task
21. 


